<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>My App</title>

  <% if (process.env.RELEASE_STAGE === 'production') { %>
    <script src="myapp-<%= version %>.js"></script>
  <% } %>

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Fira+Sans|Lato" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *,
    *:before,
    *:after {
      box-sizing: inherit;
    }
    
    html {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    html,
    body {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      min-width: 1080px;
      font: 100% sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-family: 'Fira Sans', sans-serif;
    }
    
    nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      background: #30415d;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    
    nav>.brand {
      margin: 0 20px;
    }
    
    nav>.menu {
      flex: 1;
    }
    
    nav>.menu>.item {
      margin: 0 10px;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #30415d;
      transition: all 0.2s, linear;
      color: #cdcdcd;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s, linear;
      font-family: 'Fira Sans', sans-serif;
    }
    
    nav>.menu>.item.active,
    nav>.menu>.item:hover {
      border-bottom: 3px solid #b4dbc0;
      color: #e9e9e9;
    }
    
    .user {
      background: #b4dbc0;
      padding: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      color: #30415d;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 0 10px 0 auto;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    
    .wrapper {
      min-height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-start;
      align-items: stretch;
      align-content: stretch;
    }
    
    .content-wrapper {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
    }
    
    .content {
      display: flex;
      width: 100%;
    }
    
    #main {
      flex: 1
    }
    
    #sidebar {
      width: 300px;
      margin: 0 20px;
      overflow-x: auto;
      text-align: justify;
    }
    
    footer {
      color: #cdcdcd;
      background: #30415d;
      padding: 5px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    footer a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #328cc1;
    }
    
    .spinner {
      margin: 100px auto;
      width: 50px;
      height: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 10px;
    }
    
    .spinner>div {
      background-color: #30415d;
      height: 100%;
      width: 6px;
      display: inline-block;
      -webkit-animation: sk-stretchdelay 1.2s infinite ease-in-out;
      animation: sk-stretchdelay 1.2s infinite ease-in-out;
    }
    
    .spinner .rect2 {
      -webkit-animation-delay: -1.1s;
      animation-delay: -1.1s;
    }
    
    .spinner .rect3 {
      -webkit-animation-delay: -1.0s;
      animation-delay: -1.0s;
    }
    
    @-webkit-keyframes sk-stretchdelay {
      0%,
      40%,
      100% {
        -webkit-transform: scaleY(0.4)
      }
      20% {
        -webkit-transform: scaleY(1.0)
      }
    }
    
    @keyframes sk-stretchdelay {
      0%,
      40%,
      100% {
        transform: scaleY(0.4);
        -webkit-transform: scaleY(0.4);
      }
      20% {
        transform: scaleY(1.0);
        -webkit-transform: scaleY(1.0);
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <nav>
      <a class="brand" href="#">
        <img src="https://df3gzbqk56iwk.cloudfront.net/assets/talkdesk-in-app-logotype.svg" alt="Talkdesk Logo">
      </a>

      <div class="menu">
        <a class="item active" href="#">Link1</a>
        <a class="item" href="#">Link2</a>
        <a class="item" href="#">Link3</a>
      </div>

      <div class="user">
        <span class="photo-profile">TD</span>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="content">
        <div id="main">
          <div id="myapp">
            <div class="spinner">
              <div class="rect1"></div>
              <div class="rect2"></div>
              <div class="rect3"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="sidebar">
          <h1>Sidebar</h1>
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aenean luctus nec arcu eget faucibus. Quisque porta mi
            ac dui pharetra, at pellentesque elit bibendum. Sed laoreet nunc sed lobortis molestie. Quisque et justo placerat,
            bibendum justo quis, faucibus velit. Quisque mollis mi vitae pulvinar lobortis. Vivamus id arcu nunc. Maecenas
            id ligula dictum, ultricies erat vitae, cursus sapien.</p>
          <p>Cras in est vitae mauris interdum lacinia vitae in mi. Vivamus sed diam eget mauris pellentesque lobortis. Morbi
            venenatis leo vel augue convallis blandit.</p>
          <p>Morbi scelerisque, eros at varius commodo, ipsum leo fringilla magna, id pulvinar leo est quis enim. Nunc ultrices
            metus a lectus venenatis, ut dignissim libero tempor.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
      <p>React Redux Boilerplate by <a href="https://www.talkdesk.com">Talkdesk</a></p>
    </footer>
  </div>

  <script type="text/javascript">
    document.onreadystatechange = () => {
      if (document.readyState == "complete") {
        MyApp.start(
          document.getElementById('myapp'),
          {
            id: '1',
            eventHandlers: {
              toggleSidebar: () => {
                const sidebar = document.getElementById('sidebar')
                const visible = sidebar.style.display !== 'none'
                sidebar.style.display = visible ? 'none' : 'block'
              }
            }
          }
        )
      }
    }
  </script>
</body>

</html>
